15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1024.6 of Title 21, unless there
18 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A. As used in this section:
20 1. "Adult performance" means any performance that contains
21 obscene material, if done in view of a minor or in a public place;
22 2. "Obscene material" shall have the same meaning as such term
23 is defined in subsection B of Section 1024.1 of Title 21 of the
24 Oklahoma Statutes;
